OL,4,Crescue services across Wales intensify
OL,6,FThe is facing increasing calls for a
OL,7,FWales-wide inquiry into the fire and
OL,8,Frescue service from both the Welsh
OL,9,FConservatives and Plaid Cymru.
OL,11,FThose allegations are due to be heard
OL,12,Fat an employment tribunal in Mold but
OL,13,Fnot until next month. Mr Millington
OL,14,Fdenies the allegations against him.
OL,16,FThe timing has led to questions being
OL,17,Fraised over "due diligence" during the
OL,18,Fappointment process, with Plaid
OL,19,FCymru's spokesperson for Social
OL,20,FJustice Sioned Williams describing the
OL,21,Fallegations as "deeply worrying".
