OL,6,FEducation Minister Mr Miles said: "I
OL,7,Fthink the action that Hannah Blythyn
OL,8,Fis stepping in to bring on
OL,9,Fcommissioners to take action is the
OL,10,Fright thing to do.
OL,12,F"I think she has acted very clearly."
OL,14,FWhen asked whether there should be a
OL,15,Fculture review of all the fire
OL,16,Fservices? Mr Miles said: "Every
OL,17,Forganisation in Wales needs to have a
OL,18,Fculture which is inclusive of women
OL,19,Fand does not tolerate any kind of
OL,20,Fharassment.
