OL,6,FThe Welsh Conservatives, Joel James
OL,7,FMS, Shadow Minister for Social
OL,8,FPartnership said (Mr Millington's
OL,9,Fappointment) "shows a complete lack of
OL,10,Funderstanding at the very highest
OL,11,Flevel of what needs to change".
OL,13,FHe has already written to Ms Blythyn
OL,14,Foutlining his concerns and those of
OL,15,Fresidents who have contacted him.
OL,17,FHe said: "It's been clear to everyone
OL,18,Fthat swift action was needed to tackle
OL,19,Fthe culture that was allowed to
OL,20,Fdevelop in South Wales Fire Service.
