OL,4,Crescue services across Wales intensify
OL,6,F"It is perplexing that the
OL,7,Fcommissioners feel it is acceptable to
OL,8,Fappoint an interim Chief Fire Officer
OL,9,Ffor South Wales Fire and Rescue who
OL,10,Fhimself is at the centre of bullying
OL,11,Fallegations."
OL,13,FThe ushering in of commissioners by
OL,14,Fthe Welsh Government to oversee the
OL,15,Frunning of the South Wales Fire and
OL,16,FRescue Service was meant to start a
OL,17,F"new chapter of transparency and
OL,18,Faccountability", says Sioned Williams,
OL,19,FMS.
