OL,6,FBut she said: "Instead, the fact that
OL,7,Fthere are allegations against the
OL,8,Finterim chief fire officer who was
OL,9,Fonly appointed by Commissioners last
OL,10,Fweek is deeply worrying and threatens
OL,11,Fto undermine efforts to a create new
OL,12,Fculture within the Service.
OL,14,F"Serious questions must be asked about
OL,15,Fthe due diligence taken during the
OL,16,Fappointment by the Commissioners and
OL,17,Fthe Labour Government on which they
OL,18,Facted on behalf of."
