OL,6,FShe continued: "The Commissioners and
OL,7,Fthe Deputy Minister must now
OL,8,Freconsider the appropriateness of the
OL,9,Fappointment and investigate the
OL,10,Fallegations in the short-term and as a
OL,11,Fmatter of urgency, Plaid Cymru again
OL,12,Fcall for a full review of all fire and
OL,13,Frescue services across Wales."
OL,15,FA Welsh Government spokesperson said:
OL,16,F"The Commissioners are doing important
OL,17,Fand valued work to implement the
OL,18,Fchanges needed at South Wales Fire and
OL,19,FRescue Service.
