OL,6,F"They have full powers to restructure
OL,7,Fand reform Service management and
OL,8,Finstil a positive, non-discriminatory
OL,9,Fculture. They will remain until the
OL,10,FService is demonstrably an inclusive
OL,11,Fand welcoming workplace for all.
